<lb n="0784b03"/><head type="no">No. 1689</head>
<lb n="0784b04"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead>請賓頭盧<note n="0784001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＝經【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法＝經【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784001"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">經</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0784b05"/>
<lb n="0784b06"/><byline type="Translator">宋<note n="0784002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沙門＝三藏【宮】</note><app n="0784002"><lem>沙門</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">三藏</rdg></app><note n="0784003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔釋〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔釋〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784003"><lem>釋</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>慧<note n="0784004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">簡＝蘭【宮】</note><app n="0784004"><lem>簡</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">蘭</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0784b07"/><div1 type="jing"><p>天竺國有優婆塞國王長者。<note n="0784005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝共【元】【明】</note><app n="0784005"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">共</rdg></app>設一切會。常
<lb n="0784b08"/>請賓頭盧頗羅墮誓阿羅漢賓頭盧者字也。
<lb n="0784b09"/>頗羅墮誓者姓也。其人為樹提長者現神足
<lb n="0784b10"/>故。佛擯之不聽涅槃。&CB00330;令為末法四部眾作
<lb n="0784b11"/>福田。請時於靜處燒香禮拜。向天竺摩<note n="0784006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梨＝犁【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">梨＝犁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784006"><lem>梨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">犁</rdg></app>山。
<lb n="0784b12"/>至心稱名言。大德賓頭盧頗羅墮誓。受佛教
<lb n="0784b13"/>&CB00330;。為末法人作福田。願受我請。於此處食。
<lb n="0784b14"/>若新作屋舍。亦應請之言。願受我請。於此舍
<lb n="0784b15"/>床敷<note n="0784007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">止＝上【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">止＝上【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784007"><lem>止</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">上</rdg></app>宿。若普請眾僧澡浴時。<note n="0784008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔亦〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔亦〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784008"><lem>亦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>應請之
<lb n="0784b16"/>言。願受我請。於此洗浴。及未明前具香湯淨
<lb n="0784b17"/>水澡豆楊枝。香油調<note n="0784009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">和＝適【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">和＝適【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784009"><lem>和</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">適</rdg></app>冷<note n="0784010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">暖＝煖【宮】</note><app n="0784010"><lem>暖</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">煖</rdg></app>。如人浴法。開
<lb n="0784b18"/>戶請入。然後閉戶。如人浴訖頃。眾僧乃入。
<lb n="0784b19"/>凡會食澡浴。要須一切請僧至心求解脫。不
<lb n="0784b20"/>疑不昧。信<note n="0784011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝人【宮】</note><app n="0784011"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>清淨。然後可屈。近世有<note n="0784012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【宮】</note><app n="0784012"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>長
<lb n="0784b21"/>者聞說賓頭盧阿羅漢受佛教&CB00330;為末法<note n="0784013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔人〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784013"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0784b22"/>作福田。即如法施設大會。至心請賓頭盧。氍
<lb n="0784b23"/><note n="0784014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">氀＝毹【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0784014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">氀＝毹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0784014"><lem>氀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">毹</rdg></app>下遍布華。欲以驗之。大眾食訖。發氍氀
<lb n="0784b24"/>華皆萎。懊惱自責。不知過所從來。更復精竭。
<lb n="0784b25"/>審問<note n="0784015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝法【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經＝法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784015"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>師。重設大會。如前華亦復<note n="0784016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔皆〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔皆〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784016"><lem>皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>萎。復
<lb n="0784b26"/>更傾竭盡家財產。復作大會。猶亦如前。懊惱
<lb n="0784b27"/>自責。更請百餘法師。求請所失。懺謝罪過。
<lb n="0784b28"/><note n="0784017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝始【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如＝始【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784017"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">始</rdg></app>向上座一人年老。四布悔其愆咎。上座告
<lb n="0784b29"/>之。<note n="0784018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔汝三…遮〕十七字－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0784018" word-count="17"><lem>汝三會請我。我皆受請。汝自使奴門中
<pb ed="T" id="T32.1689.0784c" n="0784c"/>
<lb n="0784c01"/>見遮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。以我年老衣服弊壞。謂是被擯。<note n="0784019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賴提＝&CB09597;渧【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賴提＝&CB09597;渧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784019"><lem>賴提</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB09597;渧</rdg></app>
<lb n="0784c02"/>沙門不<note n="0784020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">肯＝宜【元】【明】</note><app n="0784020"><lem>肯</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">宜</rdg></app>見前。我以汝請欲強入。汝奴以杖
<lb n="0784c03"/>打我。頭破額右角瘡。是第二會亦來。復不見
<lb n="0784c04"/>前。我又欲強入。復打我頭額中瘡。是第三會
<lb n="0784c05"/>亦來。如前被打。<note n="0784021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔頭〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔頭〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784021"><lem>頭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>額左角瘡。是皆汝自為
<lb n="0784c06"/>之。何所懊惋。言已不現。長者乃知是賓頭盧。
<lb n="0784c07"/>自爾<note n="0784022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784022"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>來。諸人<note n="0784023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">設＝請【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">設＝請【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784023"><lem>設</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">請</rdg></app>福皆不<note n="0784024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">敢＝須【宮】</note><app n="0784024"><lem>敢</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">須</rdg></app>復遮門。若得
<lb n="0784c08"/>賓頭盧。其坐華即不萎。若新立房舍床榻。欲
<lb n="0784c09"/>請賓頭盧時。皆當香湯灑地。燃香油燈。新床
<lb n="0784c10"/>新褥奮綿敷之。以白練覆綿上。初夜如法請
<lb n="0784c11"/>之。<note n="0784025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">還閉房戶＝閉房【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">還閉房戶＝閉房【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784025"><lem>還閉房戶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">閉房</rdg></app>。慎勿輕慢闚看。皆各至心信
<lb n="0784c12"/>其必來。精誠感徹。無不至也。來則耨上現有
<lb n="0784c13"/>臥處。浴室亦現用湯水處。受大會請時。或在
<lb n="0784c14"/>上坐。或在中坐。或在下坐。現作隨處僧形。人
<lb n="0784c15"/>求其異終不可得。去後見坐<note n="0784026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔處〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔處〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784026"><lem>處</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>華不萎乃知
<lb n="0784c16"/>之<note n="0784027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矣＝也【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">矣＝也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784027"><lem>矣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0784c17"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>請賓頭盧<note n="0784028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＝經【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法＝經【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784028"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">經</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
